IMAPAccount proton
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User jeremy@jeremyfriesen.com
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -s proton-bridge -a jeremy@jeremyfriesen.com -w"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.3

IMAPStore proton-remote
Account proton

MaildirStore proton-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Maildir/
Inbox ~/Maildir/inbox

### Sync settings
Channel proton
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Expunge Both
Create Near
Sync All
SyncState *
